content.rendered:
While I’ve not quite left the Facebook-owned Instagram, I have downloaded all my photos using the very helpful Instaport service. To Instagram’s credit, they form quite a nice little snapshot of a brief period of life.

Most of them are here for your perusal (should you choose to indulge me) and my own reminiscing.
